    <p><strong>Morlino et al. (2021)</strong> developed semi-analytic methods for solving particle transport equations at wind termination shocks. Their iterative solution technique serves as a methodological precedent for particle acceleration studies in wind- and jet-like systems.</p>

    <h2>Relevance to ArXiv Atlas</h2>
    <p>Cited by <WikiLink slug="pages/2603.16647" text="Peretti et al. (2603.16647)" /> as methodological precedent for the iterative semi-analytic solution of the transport equation at <WikiLink slug="pages/recollimation-shocks" text="recollimation shocks" />.</p>

